article:
The following is a 'list of products' branded by '[[Nokia|Nokia Corporation]]'.
This list concentrates on the modern Nokia products.

Most Nokia phones will show their model number if the user types *#0000# on its
keypad in standby mode and unlocked state, as well as its IMEI number if *#06#
is entered. The latter works on most phones available (not only for Nokias).
headings: Products marketed by Nokia Siemens Networks
